{"tid":1757290,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"曾蛇都會輸 - 陳也","createTime":"2019-11-26T12:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T13:04:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bdf3ea451430146cbb69c7c2c52c2fd0b14fea51","tid":1757290,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:31:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191126/20813352/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191126%2F20813352%2F&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx934WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=99f3afad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191126%2F20813352%2F&h=593bc3ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191126/20813352/</a><br />\n<br />\n曾蛇都會輸 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191126/large/1574670104_a722.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191126%2Flarge%2F1574670104_a722.jpg&h=f2170c03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾偉雄聯合國筍job，大熱倒灶？天方夜譚吧。<br />\n<br />\n你冇發夢，曾經聯署撳極個sign掣都無動於衷，後來被告之，有網軍作祟（王立強先生可以詳細話你知），癱瘓了聯署。再後來呢，聯署重來一次！這一趟，和你sign，HKers冇含過一滴淚，成功爭取。<br />\n<br />\n電子投票，得咗。肉身實體投票呢？排成港珠澳橋的蛇餅，身旁左右都係老海鮮，又點？這一票，習慣用屎忽度屎橋的689，跟又試唔肯食藥打回原形的國師一樣見識。兩條廢柴，叫食晒二噁英的各區選民，不投泛民的po，兜不攏，無位入。<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">另一些平日扮黃的KOL，同樣好肉緊，鬧晒泛民和素人。</span></span>何以這些廢柴會認為，還有人聽他們指點大嶼山？喪噏當秘笈的時代過去了，fb追溯唔使特朗普講的「解放軍入城摧毀香港只需14分鐘」，兩分鐘就夠。<span style=\"color: orange;\">這些人渣花口水勸人唔投，目測嘴部動作僵硬，也就是說，票，是可以改變社區，落地開花的。</span>建制不能靠口水，要政權灌水，泛民與年輕素人就是要扭轉花灑頭，扭斷西灣河醜怪紅頂文化廣場、屯門騎呢山墳、元朗天價17億行人天橋的複製詐騙大水喉。打大佬係艱難嘅，不過狂言警隊道歉為風土病的曾蛇都會落選，勇和，盡做。 <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n==============<br />\n<br />\n陳也好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94fef2941da50de6fcaf8d5d8409beb825854dfd","tid":1757290,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oSUX0Rg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoSUX0Rg.jpg&h=b36b87af&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}